snippet.title: Note Ban Day 38: 'No Cash' Boards Anger Bank Customers in Malda

localized.description:
Note Ban Day 38: 'No cash' boards anger bank customers in Malda. Angry people throw stones on SBI bank branch after not getting the cash. RBI governor Urjit Patel was shown black flags in West Bengal.
